VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'A few weeks ago, I tweeted that there will be at least one open-source image editor that\'s as good as Nano Banana. Well, ladies and gentlemen, the moment is finally here. So, Alibaba just released Quen image edit 259, which'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'stands for September of 2025. This is their best and latest image editor. And from my initial tests, it\'s as good or even better than Nano Banana. So, in'

[00:24] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this video, I\'m going to go over all the cool things it can do, plus its limitations. And of course, I\'m going to show you where and how to use it, and step-by-step how to download it on your computer so you can run it for free'

[00:37] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'offline for unlimited times. Let\'s jump right in. Thanks to HubSpot for sponsoring this video. So, I\'ll link to this official announcement page in the description below. This is essentially an image editor just like Nano Banana'

[00:51] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'where you can upload any reference photos and prompt it to do anything with those photos. So, for example, you can upload these two photos and generate some wedding photos of them. If you\'re a'

[01:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'wedding photographer, I would be slightly worried if I were you. Now, this new Quen image edit is way better at actually preserving character consistency. So, for example, we can upload this background and this'

[01:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'character and basically get her to sit on this chair. And here is what we get. Or we can upload this background and get her to sit in the cafe like this. Notice that all of the details of this cafe are'

[01:30] [scene:talk]
